data.description: Welcome to Overlook Avenue on Browns Point. Nestled in a serene setting with Puget Sound views, this remodeled rambler with basement is the epitome of understated luxury. Step inside and be greeted by an abundance of natural light flooding this spacious floor plan. The meticulously designed kitchen is curated with sleek JENNAIR high-end appliances, custom cabinetry & waterfall quartz countertop edge perfect for the culinary enthusiast. Two king size primary bedrooms, each offering an oasis of comfort & style, along with spa-like bathrooms and walkin closets. Versatile spaces are ideal for multigenerational living and work from home set-ups. Dine al fresco or relax & unwind after a long day on the West facing view decks. EV ready garage too!
